{"TopicId":207216,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Space plane wing area and hard to rotate","CreatedByName":"Hatsune","CreatedById":196694,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T21:29:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Hatsune","CreatedById":196694,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T21:29:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy CG and CL are close together, I have 120 ton takeoff weight\u002B23 wing area. I have two regular elevons\u002B1 standard canard on each side. My space plane flies well, but I am having a hard time rotating it. Is it because my landing gear is too far back, not enough pitch control surfaces, or I don\u0027t have enough lift?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T21:34:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPictures would help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wizard Kerbal","CreatedById":209063,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T21:35:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis could be many issues, but in your case it\u2019s likely too few control surfaces/too little lift.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImages of the craft always help!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hatsune","CreatedById":196694,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T21:40:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224101258\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207216\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221646948086\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210816\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Admiral Fluffy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Admiral Fluffy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPictures would help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow to I insert picture?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T21:41:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThread moved to Gameplay questions, where hopefully pictures will be forthcoming shortly.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hatsune","CreatedById":196694,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T21:42:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224101263\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207216\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221646948470\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThread moved to Gameplay questions, where hopefully pictures will be forthcoming shortly.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am trying to put picture, but I don\u0027t see an option to do so\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scarecrow71","CreatedById":210112,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T21:43:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224101265\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207216\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221646948536\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022196694\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hatsune\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Hatsune said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am trying to put picture, but I don\u0027t see an option to do so\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpload the image to your hosting site of choice (Imgur is a good one), then copy the link from there and paste it into your message here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hatsune","CreatedById":196694,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T21:45:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPosted, I figured that out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-03-10T21:58:21Z\u0022 title=\u002203/10/2022 09:58  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 10, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Hatsune\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hatsune","CreatedById":196694,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T21:57:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022JDirmtX.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/JDirmtX.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00223nVflGb.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/3nVflGb.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022BkKDEbA.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/BkKDEbA.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"18Watt","CreatedById":198538,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-10T22:14:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nLanding gear looks to be in a good location, but try moving it forward if you can.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nMove the canard pitch surfaces farther forward, closer to the nose.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe elevators should be larger, and mounting them farther aft would also help. \u00A0For a plane that size I would use the Big-S elevators.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-03-10T22:15:42Z\u0022 title=\u002203/10/2022 10:15  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 10, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by 18Watt\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerikBalm","CreatedById":91917,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-11T09:16:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou seem to have zero \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Angle of Attack\u0022\u003EAoA\u003C/abbr\u003E, meaning that your wings are producing no lift on the runway. That will make it very hard to lift the nose up with just the force from the elevons.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry using the offset tool to raise/lower landing gear as appropriate to that your nose points up a bit when on the runway. Also consider just giving your wings some incidence,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}